de.charite.compbio.jannovar.pedigree

Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.charite.compbio.jannovar.pedigree.Person

  • public final class Person
extends Object
    An individual from a pedigree file, Java programmer friendly version. Note that a Person is not truly immutable since its mother and father field have to be non-final during its construction. However, since the members only have package visibility, Person is immutable for all practical considerations after construction.
    Author:
    Peter N Robinson, Manuel Holtgrewe
